@mainpage           Roku %LT Operating System API Reference

@section intro Introduction

<p>Roku %LT is a new operating system for tiny embedded devices.</p>
<p style="bottom-margin: 0em">Roku %LT supports:</p>
<ol style="margin-top: -1.1em">
<li>a minimum processor configuration of 100Mhz</li>
<li>a minimum RAM configuration of 64KiB (65,536 bytes)</li>
<li>hosting on top of full-featured devices and operating systems, for example
Roku OS devices, Windows and iOS, and game consoles.</li>
</ol>

<p>The %LT Operating System is grouped into <b>%LT Libraries</b>.<br>
This is API reference documentation for the libraries that
comprise the <b>Standard %LT Operating System Distribution.</b></p>

